	<div id="search"><!--search_terms--><a name="search"></a>[!AjaxSearch? &ajaxSearch=`1` &landingPage=`8` &moreResultsPage=`8` &addJscript=`0` &showIntro=`0` &ajaxMax=`5` &extract=`1`!]</div>
